        └── hoa-loan-readiness-checklist.pdf
```

### SEO Technical Requirements
- Generate XML sitemap automatically on build
- Include Open Graph + Twitter Card meta for all pages
- Implement canonical URLs to avoid duplicate content
- Add JSON-LD schema: Article, FAQPage, HowTo as appropriate
- Internal link every content page to the main intake form
- Implement breadcrumb navigation with schema markup
- Page speed: target 90+ Lighthouse score (critical for rankings)
- Mobile-first responsive design

### State-First Architecture (Anti-Doorway Strategy)
Do NOT create hundreds of "HOA loans in [city]" pages. Instead:
- Create state-level hub pages with materially unique statutory/compliance content
- Each state page must contain: state-specific regulations, local resources, real process differences
- Only expand to city-level if there's genuinely unique local content
- This avoids Google's doorway page penalties while still capturing geo intent

